Resource Profile: Debt Portal Invoice

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/DebtPortalInvoice Version: 1.4.10
Active as of 2025-04-18 Computable Name: DebtPortalInvoice

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE (430) to Invoice.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Debt Portal PaymentReconciliation
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: Lung Cancer Screening
